  Restart

  sudo systemctl restart siem-agent

  Loglarni ko'rish (jonli)

  sudo journalctl -u siem-agent -f

  Loglarni ko'rish (oxirgi 50 qator)

  sudo journalctl -u siem-agent -n 50

